# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  MathGPT .env Configuration
#  Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual values
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── LLM Providers (choose one primary, one fallback) ─────────────────

# NVIDIA NIM API (Primary — get from build.nvidia.com)
# Sign up: https://build.nvidia.com/
# Recommended for best math reasoning
NVIDIA_API_KEY=your_nvidia_api_key_here

# Groq API (Fallback — free tier available)
# Sign up: https://console.groq.com/
# No rate limits on free tier, fast inference
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# ── Optional: Supabase (for session persistence) ─────────────────────

# Get from: https://supabase.com/
# Required for CloudSQL session history (optional)
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key_here

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Setup Instructions:
# 1. Get NVIDIA_API_KEY from https://build.nvidia.com/
# 2. Get GROQ_API_KEY from https://console.groq.com/
# 3. (Optional) Get SUPABASE_URL + SUPABASE_KEY from https://supabase.com/
# 4. Copy this file to .env and fill in your keys
# 5. Run: streamlit run app.py
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
